page.title: 18SATURDAY WITH THE WARRENS
page.content: On Saturday I woke up, went down stairs and made the breakfast. While my scramble egg was cooking, I put on my T shirt and jeans. I went to see the gerbils who were out. After that I played ball with Shep and hide and seek. Then we took Shep for a walk. When we came home my mum said we could go swimming so we drove off but when we got to HMS Dryad it was shut so we went home. It was lunch time so we had our lunch. Then my mum decided to go to the beach. When we got there we walked on the shore and I saw ten dead cuttlefish and we collected shells. After that we went home to bed.
